Subject: selftests/sched_ext: Add test for sched_ext dl_server

Add a selftest to validate the correct behavior of the deadline server
for the ext_sched_class.

Reviewed-by: Emil Tsalapatis <emil@xxxxxxxxxx>
Tested-by: Christian Loehle <christian.loehle@xxxxxxxxxx>
Co-developed-by: Joel Fernandes <joelagnelf@xxxxxxxxxx>
